---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms & Conditions"
  description="Terms and Conditions of Sonia Buddy for website and mobile app users, bus timetable information, route search, vehicle rental listings, third-party services and user responsibilities."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p>Effective Date: April 19, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> April 19, 2026</p>
        <p>
          These Terms and Conditions ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the Sonia Buddy mobile application
          and related website, collectively called the "Service". By downloading, installing, accessing, or using
          Sonia Buddy, you agree to be legally bound by these Terms. If you do not agree with these Terms, you must
          discontinue use of the Service immediately.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is a West Bengal travel information and service listing platform. Our Service helps users
          search bus timetable information, route details, stop information, direct and indirect travel options,
          and driver-included vehicle rental listings such as car rental, bus rental, toto rent, pickup van,
          ambulance, wedding bus, tour car and school bus services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>
          You must be at least 18 years of age to register for or use Sonia Buddy, especially for account creation,
          booking requests, rental enquiries, owner listing submission, or direct communication with service providers.
        </p>
        <p>
          By using the Service, you represent and warrant that you meet this age requirement and have the legal
          capacity to enter into a binding agreement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>2. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information, including your name, email address,
          phone number and address entered manually, where required for account creation, bookings, rental enquiries,
          listing submission, support, or communication.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all
          activities that occur under your account.
        </p>
        <p>
          You agree to notify Sonia Buddy immediately of any unauthorized access to or use of your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>3. Service Accuracy and Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          Bus timings, routes, stops, middle-stop suggestions, direct routes, indirect routes and location
          information provided in West Bengal are estimates compiled from publicly available, user-submitted
          and operator-provided data.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, availability, or real-time precision of any
          schedule, route, stop, fare, travel time, GPS location, or operator information.
        </p>
        <p>
          Bus timings may change due to traffic, weather, road conditions, local events, holidays, operator changes,
          breakdowns, strikes, or other reasons. Users are strongly advised to arrive at the bus stop 10–15 minutes
          before the scheduled time and verify important travel details locally when needed.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not liable for delays, missed buses, lost time, missed appointments, financial loss,
          or any direct or consequential loss arising from traffic, operator changes, GPS inaccuracies, or reliance
          on timetable information.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>4. Third-Party Services and Tour Bookings</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy operates as a platform that connects users with independent local travel agencies, vehicle
          owners, drivers, ambulance providers, goods transport providers and tour operators.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not responsible for the quality, safety, legality, availability, pricing, refund, cancellation,
          behavior, delay, or delivery of services provided by any third-party tour operator, agency, owner,
          driver, or service provider.
        </p>
        <p>
          All financial transactions, refunds, cancellations, bookings, rental discussions and disputes relating
          to tours, rentals, transport services, or vehicle services must be resolved directly between the user
          and the respective agency, owner, driver, or service provider.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>5. Vehicle Rental Listings</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy may display driver-included rental listings for cars, buses, toto, auto, pickup vans,
          ambulances, wedding vehicles, tour vehicles, school-office vehicles and goods transport vehicles.
        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not a transport company, taxi operator, ambulance operator, vehicle owner, or travel agency.
          We do not directly provide rental vehicles, drivers, ambulance services, tours, or transport services.
        </p>
        <p>
          Users must directly confirm final price, vehicle condition, driver details, pickup location, route,
          availability, extra charges, cancellation rules, documents, permits and insurance before confirming
          any rental or booking.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>6. Ambulance and Emergency Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy may show ambulance or emergency vehicle listings submitted by owners or service providers.
          Sonia Buddy does not operate ambulance services and does not guarantee emergency response, medical
          assistance, ambulance arrival time, driver availability, or hospital coordination.
        </p>
        <p>
          In a medical emergency, users should contact official emergency numbers, nearby hospitals, local ambulance
          services, or local authorities directly. Sonia Buddy should not be treated as an emergency medical service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>7. Prohibited Use</h2>
        <p>When using Sonia Buddy, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use the Service for any unlawful, fraudulent, abusive, harmful, or misleading purpose.</li>
          <li>Attempt to hack, reverse engineer, decompile, disassemble, scrape, copy, or tamper with the app, website, database, or infrastructure.</li>
          <li>Submit false, misleading, spam, duplicate, malicious, or unauthorized route, schedule, stop, listing, or booking information.</li>
          <li>Use automated means such as bots, scrapers, crawlers, or bulk extraction tools to access or copy any part of the Service without written permission.</li>
          <li>Upload illegal, offensive, copyrighted, fake, misleading, or unauthorized photos or content.</li>
          <li>Misuse another person's contact number, identity, business name, vehicle details, or listing information.</li>
          <li>Harass, threaten, abuse, cheat, or mislead other users, owners, drivers, agencies, or Sonia Buddy staff.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>8. Owner and Listing Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>
          Vehicle owners, drivers, agencies and service providers who submit listings are responsible for providing
          accurate and lawful information, including vehicle type, photos, service city, contact number, WhatsApp
          number, price text, seats or capacity, availability and description.
        </p>
        <p>
          Owners must not upload false, copied, misleading, abusive, illegal, or unauthorized photos or information.
          Sonia Buddy may review, edit, reject, hide, suspend, or remove any listing if it appears fake, unsafe,
          misleading, outdated, duplicate, spammy, or harmful to users.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
