        </p>
        <p>
          Sonia Buddy is not liable for delays, accidents, cancellations, service failures, wrong information,
          payment disputes, refund disputes, owner behavior, driver behavior, vehicle condition, emergency outcomes,
          or any loss caused by third-party service providers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>13. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>
          You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Sonia Buddy, its owners, team members, partners, service
