        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>14. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website or app may contain links to third-party websites, phone numbers, WhatsApp links, maps,
          service provider pages, payment pages, or external resources. Sonia Buddy is not responsible for the
          content, policies, safety, accuracy, or practices of those third-party services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>15. Modifications to the Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Updated Terms will be posted on this page with
          a revised effective date. Your continued use of the Service after any such changes constitutes acceptance
